---
import { Shield, Zap, Thermometer } from '@lucide/astro';
---

<section class="cl-intro">
  <div class="inner">
    <div class="cl-intro-grid">
      <div class="cl-intro-text">
        <div class="section-eyebrow reveal">What is Weld Overlay Cladding?</div>
        <h2 class="section-title reveal">Corrosion Protection<br>at Production Speed</h2>
        <p class="section-lead reveal">
          Weld overlay cladding applies ERNiCrMo-3 (Alloy 625) to component surfaces
          for corrosion protection, hard-facing, and surface repair. The TwinWire RapidClad 2.0
          delivers this at unprecedented deposition rates while maintaining the lowest
          dilution in the industry.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="cl-intro-cards">
        <div class="cl-card reveal">
          <div class="cl-card-icon"><Shield size={24} /></div>
          <div>
            <strong>Corrosion Resistant Overlay</strong>
            <span>Alloy 625 layers provide long-term protection for pipelines, valves, flanges, and other critical containment components.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="cl-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <div class="cl-card-icon"><Zap size={24} /></div>
          <div>
            <strong>Highest Deposition Rate</strong>
            <span>Up to <span class="u-imp">20 lbs/hr</span><span class="u-met">9.1 kg/hr</span> — dramatically outperforming standard TIG and hot wire methods.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="cl-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <div class="cl-card-icon"><Thermometer size={24} /></div>
          <div>
            <strong>Lowest Dilution</strong>
            <span>80% reduced dilution rates maintain overlay chemistry with minimal base metal mixing.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cl-intro {
    padding: 110px 60px;
    background: var(--bg);
  }

  .inner {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .cl-intro-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .section-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--sapphire);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .section-eyebrow::before {
    content: '';
    display: block;
    width: 24px;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--sapphire);
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--black);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .section-lead {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--gray-mid);
    line-height: 1.75;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .cl-intro-cards {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .cl-card {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--gray-light);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 28px 24px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .cl-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--sapphire-mid);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(27, 58, 140, 0.08);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .cl-card-icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    min-width: 48px;
    background: var(--sapphire-light);
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--sapphire);
  }

  .cl-card strong {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--black);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .cl-card span {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--gray-mid);
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  @media (max-width: 960px) {
    .cl-intro { padding: 72px 24px; }
    .cl-intro-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 48px;
    }
  }
</style>
